<ThingDef ParentName="BaseHumanMakeableGun">
    <defName>DRKGun_SemelePlasmaRifle</defName>
    <label>SEMELE plasma rifle</label>
    <description>SEMELE was the original project designed to replace the Winchester P94 plasma caster. Although it was stolen by REPCONN Aerospace, the technology and design specification used in SEMELE, specifically the Heisenberg compensation field when dealing with matter conversion, was later used to develop RobCo Industries' own model of the plasma rifle. This iteration proved to be successful enough for deployment in the Enclave Armed Forces.</description>
